[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST jumps in \Hs, showing a good suit and slam interest.

EAST has great \H support so bids RKCB 4NT.

WEST responds 5\S, showing two Key Cards and the \HQ.

That is enough for EAST to bid the slam.}

